      "Text": "Security update for mariadb",
      "Title": "Topic",
      "Type": "Summary"
    },
    {
      "Text": "This update for mariadb fixes the following issue:\n\n- Update to v11.8.6\n- CVE-2026-32710: heap-based buffer overflow via `JSON_SCHEMA_VALID()` can lead to crash or remote code execution (bsc#1260081).\n",
